data.description: RIVER OAKS FOR $499,900 ALL ON ONE FLOOR ARE 4 VERY NICE SIZED BEDROOMS, WALK-IN CLOSETS, GREAT LOCATION JUST ONE BLOCK WEST OF THE GERMANTOWN LINE.  FRESH INTERIOR PAINT, NEW CARPET, ABUNDANT NATURAL LIGHT COMING IN TO LARGE GREAT ROOM WITH VAULTED CEILING, PAINTED STONE FIREPLACE AND LOTS OF STORAGE. KITCHEN OPENS INTO THE GREAT ROOM AND HAS A SEPARATE BREAKFAST ROOM. UPDATED BATHROOMS. SELLERS HAVE CAREFULLY PREPARED FOR THE NEXT OWNER. SOME ROOMS ARE VIRTUALLY STAGED.
